column5: This maight be the coolest dining room table I've ever seen. http://www.gizmodo.com/gadgets/home-entert...rmer-220695.php

Wow,what a table....Its mezmorizing just watching it work !!!!
Cool table would be great for poker as well.
wow someone put a lot of thought into that.....
